	generateApplyMethodsWithContext): Likewise.
	(generateApplyMethodsWithoutContext): Pass incoming Variable to
	CheckedTarget.emitCheckedCoerceif there is one.
	* LetExp.java (compile): Coerce value using CheckedTarget.

