	* FindTailCalls.java (walklambdaExp):  Set CANNOT_INLINE for
	class methods.
	* ModuleExp.java (allocFields):  A ClassExp always gets a field,
	even if it is private.
	* SetExp.java (compile):  Call compileSetField for a ClassExp
	even if it is private.

